  "title": "Senior Interior Designer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Senior Interior Designer (Full time l Singapore)</strong></p><p><em>Role Description:</em></p><p>We are seeking a full-time Senior Interior Designer to involves space planning, creating construction drawings, designing interiors, and selecting and specifying furniture, fixtures, and equipment (FF&E).</p><p>The Senior Designers will collaborate with the team and clients to resolve practical challenges and bring flair to each project.</p><p><em>Job Responsibilities:</em></p><ul><li>Interpret programming established by Director and Client and enforce with team.</li><li>Assist, generate and guide compelling conceptual design narratives and concepts</li><li>Assist in space planning from town planning phases to final documentation submissions</li><li>Assist in managing and guiding client expectations, team communication, and consultant coordination</li><li>Guide and mentor staff yet helping the team and provide a “hands on” approach when necessary to ensure project deadlines and Hachem design levels are met.</li><li>Provide project team coordination for the documentation, specifications, and material selections required for construction</li></ul><p><strong>How to Apply</strong></p><p>Please send your CV and portfolio (10MB max or link) to:</p><p> 📧 careers@hachem.com.au<br /></p><p>Portfolio must include:</p><ul><li>Hotel design experience (required for both roles).</li><li>Clear and detailed documentation.</li></ul>",
